Homocysteing Reagent Pack:
1. 1 Bottle (4.5mL) Pretreatment Soution.
2. 1 Bottle (10.5mL) S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine Hydrolase.

4. 1 Bottle (10.5mL) S-adenosyl-L-cysteine Tracer.

3 Bottles (2.5mL each of L-H) of Homocysteine Controls, 7-12.5-25 μmol/L.
